{"id": "1193564774500409355", "channel_id": "1193564774500409355", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "我們認為相位對弈（beta）主要存在三個問題。\n\n- 獎勵被迫感強：有豐厚的獎勵並且還有獨有的商店貨幣，以至於大家不得不去遊玩。\n- 遊戲可用組合少：喚醒體數量過於有限，許多喜愛的角色無法出場，以至於場面和體驗對策都比較單一。\n- 對策克制樂趣少：目前喚醒體的技能組更多是還原普通模式的技能組，作為整個遊戲的戰術互動克制並不完整。\n\n對於V1.0相位對弈beta給大家帶來不夠好的體驗，我們非常抱歉！\n\n我們會盡快在先解決第一個問題，取消相位對弈的各項獨有獎勵，獎勵與幻夢深潛完全並軌，讓大家平時只需要在幻夢深潛與相位對弈中選擇自己喜歡的模式即可。\n\n至於剩下兩個問題，我們將大幅度重新設計來解決。但這不會很快到來。在此前，我們會先維持最低限度的平衡與錯誤修復工作。", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T14:40:17.602000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": true, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 12}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193564774500409355", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關於「相位對弈（beta）」的計畫", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193566817470390374", "channel_id": "1193564774500409355", "type": 0, "author_id": "1119678312130822275", "author_name": "pokai2228", "author_bot": false, "content": "哇跟幻夢合併太好了你們真棒我愛你們😘😘", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T14:48:24.684000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193564774500409355", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關於「相位對弈（beta）」的計畫", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193572593345769593", "channel_id": "1193564774500409355", "type": 0, "author_id": "857891931253374986", "author_name": "jojosir.", "author_bot": false, "content": "其他游戏的pvp一般分数高时会有称号头像鼓励高玩，普通玩家打场数换满道具。可能排名会影响抽卡资源，但是商店资源都缺就太不合适了。", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T15:11:21.760000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193564774500409355", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關於「相位對弈（beta）」的計畫", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193576098584346714", "channel_id": "1193564774500409355", "type": 0, "author_id": "1193455249088852028", "author_name": "yinlingdang", "author_bot": false, "content": "現在的pvp，再放專屬獎勵不太合適。\n不過稱號頭像這種確實可以有。", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T15:25:17.474000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193564774500409355", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關於「相位對弈（beta）」的計畫", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193576292872896562", "channel_id": "1193564774500409355", "type": 0, "author_id": "998266367650308108", "author_name": "banano.2", "author_bot": false, "content": "同意頭像跟稱號可以有～\n太好了PVP玩家跟PVE玩家各取所需，德政", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T15:26:03.796000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193564774500409355", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關於「相位對弈（beta）」的計畫", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
