{"id": "1193578790387994654", "channel_id": "1193564774500409355", "type": 0, "author_id": "786616136678506496", "author_name": "ganxiyu06", "author_bot": false, "content": "合併好評", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T15:35:59.250000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193564774500409355", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關於「相位對弈（beta）」的計畫", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193579643270332477", "channel_id": "1193564774500409355", "type": 0, "author_id": "857891931253374986", "author_name": "jojosir.", "author_bot": false, "content": "还有一点需要强调，即使在之后进行调整，本赛季的玩家也已经收到了不正确的对待，我认为是需要考虑补偿的。可能其他玩家对此不敏感，但我觉得很有必要提一下。\n以官方鼓励的资深一（但是未必所有人都已经达到）和实际最高的段位对比，总共差了1400银芯和14抽普池。普通玩家看到这些资源会感到落差，而如果补偿，又会让重pvp玩家感到不平衡。其实是非常难做的。", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T15:39:22.593000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193564774500409355", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關於「相位對弈（beta）」的計畫", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193579974217699438", "channel_id": "1193564774500409355", "type": 0, "author_id": "857891931253374986", "author_name": "jojosir.", "author_bot": false, "content": "然后，和深潜合并，但是合并后完成周常和日常所需的次数也需要尽快确定。假如我不想玩pvp/不想打深潜，需要每天/每周多少把，才能拿齐能拿到的资源。", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T15:40:41.497000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193564774500409355", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關於「相位對弈（beta）」的計畫", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193588628857815182", "channel_id": "1193564774500409355", "type": 19, "author_id": "870225701855436801", "author_name": "ahuahuahua", "author_bot": false, "content": "可能可以高段位玩家多補償代幣…嗎？", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T16:15:04.924000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193579643270332477", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193564774500409355", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關於「相位對弈（beta）」的計畫", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193602140468420688", "channel_id": "1193564774500409355", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "頭像這類無關養成戰鬥的內容是未來可能會作為獎勵放入的，希望大家能夠接受。", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:08:46.343000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["857891931253374986"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193572593345769593", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193564774500409355", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關於「相位對弈（beta）」的計畫", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193602591926521898", "channel_id": "1193564774500409355", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "這一點可能各方面都會比較難，各方群體感受都不同。直接取消未來賽季可能更合適。", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:10:33.979000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["857891931253374986"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193579643270332477", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193564774500409355", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關於「相位對弈（beta）」的計畫", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193602670414540901", "channel_id": "1193564774500409355", "type": 19, "author_id": "1186905815479758868", "author_name": "h1821260388", "author_bot": false, "content": "無關養成的資源大家肯定都能接受的，因為所有的遊戲都這麼做。大佬拿到了有排面，平民沒拿到也不影響養成，雙贏局面。換句話說，這才是安排獎勵的正確方式，也就是我說的金字塔型。頂層放養成無關的獎勵，底層放大家都需要的資源", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:10:52.692000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193602140468420688", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193564774500409355", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關於「相位對弈（beta）」的計畫", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
