{"id": "1193601164311265320", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "1186905815479758868", "author_name": "h1821260388", "author_bot": false, "content": "我希望總獎勵應該是金字塔型，越往上獎勵越少越不重要，越往下獎勵越多。大部分人都是集中在金字塔底部的，只有少數玩家會往上打。如果把重要的,稀缺的资源放在顶部，就必然造成被逼迫感", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:04:53.609000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193601360055255181", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "1186905815479758868", "author_name": "h1821260388", "author_bot": false, "content": "就像現有的pvp一樣，越往上獎勵越多，這完全背離了群眾，必然引發不滿", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:05:40.278000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193601648757592174", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "理解考量。對於當前玩家，正好有時間原點道具可以幫助大家重新分配。獎勵方面確定更多細節後再與大家分享。重置功能則可能不會提供，否則獎勵就只能最後拿這樣，除非大家呼聲很高，接受最後拿獎勵？", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:06:49.110000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["190674373483429888"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193581956613546054", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193601896649338940", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "謝謝意見，大方向來說會是這樣！", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:07:48.212000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1186905815479758868"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193601164311265320", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193603985924440064", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 19, "author_id": "190674373483429888", "author_name": ".weiyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "我就擔心會是這樣......通常附帶重置功能的鎖角系統，\n就是允許多次挑戰，但只紀錄成績最好的那次兌獎，\n沒有的話就會變成要謹慎考慮打完結算的時機\n\n不想一個不小心被鎖到後續戰鬥無解，\n戰力不足的玩家最好等待勇者們探明各路虛實再上\n\n好玩我覺得是好玩的，但門檻可不低", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:16:06.334000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193601648757592174", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193604909753442304", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "所以你的意見是看來還是提供重置比較好？", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:19:46.592000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["190674373483429888"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193603985924440064", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193605765605372055", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 19, "author_id": "190674373483429888", "author_name": ".weiyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "坦白說我擔心的是這樣做，\n對目前的主流玩家而言負擔會太重，\n我個人當然是想玩更好玩的，\n但會擔心能享受這種遊戲方式的玩家數量，\n能否支撐這個遊戲健康走下去\n\n這中間的尺度把握，我想需要官方那邊的數據、經驗來判斷，\n作為一名用戶，我只是在提供一個用戶的意見", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:23:10.643000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193604909753442304", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193606622984016043", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "了解你的意見，我們也同樣非常擔心，因此才提前進行說明。這個玩法變化有助於緩解遊戲的多方面問題，包括平衡性、長草期等。但壓力確實會比較大，獎勵與要求方面還有很多需要仔細思考的地方。我們會繼續謹慎研究，謝謝！", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:26:35.058000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:26:53.468000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["190674373483429888"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193605765605372055", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193608012741484746", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "190674373483429888", "author_name": ".weiyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "嗯，如果是要採用帶重置的設計，\n我想像中是像這樣的形式：\n\n玩家必須依次挑戰35 40 45 50...的關卡，\n並在每次成功通關後獲取分配給該關卡的獎勵，\n每次打完一關會將挑戰用的陣容鎖定\n\n但在挑戰完整輪後（比方這次卡在60，通關失敗），\n玩家若在期間角色獲得提升or拉了新角色，\n希望重新分配通過前面關卡的陣容，\n則可以使用**重置**功能，將進度回歸到挑戰35的狀態\n\n已獲取的獎勵部分無須退回，玩家要想爭取更高的獎勵，\n則需要優化這次挑戰的配置，\n用更少、更針對的陣容去應對前期關卡，\n以求這次順利攻破更高的階層，\n這樣探路的成本就不會那麼大，\n也可避免不小心鎖錯角、沒考慮到特定Boss的難點，\n以至於提早死局，直接罰站到下一期的情況\n\n這樣的話，獎勵也是每次成績更好就可以到手", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:32:06.402000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:57:08.492000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193608742265163796", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "190674373483429888", "author_name": ".weiyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "<:wubbaboo_lazy:1114557418769235998>", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:35:00.334000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193608885672628365", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "456226577798135808", "author_name": "Deleted User", "author_bot": false, "content": "<:shark:794103333081579530>", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:35:34.525000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193608964101906562", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "190674373483429888", "author_name": ".weiyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "至於無重置的鎖角就很刺激了，要馬需要謹慎的探路，\n要馬需要先鋒攻略組的努力付出，\n也許有助於核心玩家的社群活躍", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:35:53.224000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:36:57.817000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193609053595779162", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "190674373483429888", "author_name": ".weiyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "但總覺得受眾會是肉眼可見的縮小", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:36:14.561000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193609122097152101", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "190674373483429888", "author_name": ".weiyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "<:Sui_smile:858411125238661140>", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:36:30.893000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193609649564418058", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "456226577798135808", "author_name": "Deleted User", "author_bot": false, "content": "<:sleep:1005054699222880277>", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:38:36.651000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193610985496379433", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "190674373483429888", "author_name": ".weiyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "我的想法大概就這樣，該怎麼抉擇還請製作組斟酌，\n也多收集其他玩家的意見，\n畢竟我肯定沒有貴團隊懂自家的遊戲，\n也沒法擔負任何責任", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T17:43:55.162000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193616211234258954", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "804439198655971351", "author_name": "sktd", "author_bot": false, "content": "个人观点看就是步子跨太大了。一个才开服一个多月的游戏，就要求24个人都要有接近35级以上的练度。制作组应该在服务器能看到玩家手上角色的数量。先不说练度，目前能凑齐24角色的玩家数量比例大概有多少？能有10%？还是5%？或者甚至是1%？你们可以统计下信息。\n\n另外，即使不佩戴任何命轮，又假设真的又有24个角色，但是所有角色都需要经验和突破材料等等吧，这些总共的材料又是什么量级？有具体计算过吗？我大概脑测了一下就感觉是天文数字。更不用说周本材料，一个月下来才有几个，24个人怎么分？如果不买大月卡的话，培养时间将会是更加漫长的过程，到时候又多了一个逼氪的节奏。\n\n解决方案我之前也说过了\n（1）提供全角色试用，就算没该角色也能借。好友助战只能缓解一点角色数量的压力，但通常顶多只能借几个人，不如直接提供全角色试用。\n（2）或者降低关卡数量到3，对应人数只需要12人，大大降低了培养材料的需求。随着游戏运营时间的增加，再逐步开放后续的关卡。总之不要这一步跨太大，慢慢改革不好吗？", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:04:41.075000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193616585953390714", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "804439198655971351", "author_name": "sktd", "author_bot": false, "content": "还有一个很明显的反馈，同样是发表在校猫日志，这条内容评论数最多，但几乎没有表情包点赞，这代表了几乎没人认同这一举措。", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:06:10.415000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193617541013184603", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "1176579168448823471", "author_name": "llhwwc_89248", "author_bot": false, "content": "24个角色实在是太多了", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:09:58.119000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193617687159517194", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "1176579168448823471", "author_name": "llhwwc_89248", "author_bot": false, "content": "至少应当允许少量角色有重复使用1次的机会", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:10:32.963000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193617739093397675", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "1084923460326793289", "author_name": "tofu0834", "author_bot": false, "content": "我覺得角色試用是可以參考的方案。24人說真的還是有點多，更不用說關卡需求一定練度。並且提供角色試用可以減少玩家在交友方面的壓力。（另外，角色試用還有一個潛在的優點是可以讓玩家事先體驗某些角色的使用方法與現有隊伍契合度，所以就算不能提供所有的角色試用也可以提供當期up的角色試用等，對於角色使用方法的開發與推廣應該也有所幫助。）", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:10:45.345000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:17:49.271000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193618201754476615", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "1084923460326793289", "author_name": "tofu0834", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且我覺得最佳的遊戲難度應該是建立於操作與配隊等策略之上的，而不是考驗玩家的角色「數量」。", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:12:35.652000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
