{"id": "1193619881162178772", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 19, "author_id": "1176579168448823471", "author_name": "llhwwc_89248", "author_bot": false, "content": "比如允许玩家选择4队/5队/6队拿去不同档次的奖励？", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:19:16.054000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193618391697731676", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193620056232448160", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "1176579168448823471", "author_name": "llhwwc_89248", "author_bot": false, "content": "有条件组6队的玩家吃满奖励，没有条件的玩家组出4队应该还是压力不大的，亏些奖励但也能够完整参与玩法，提供一定的弹性", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:19:57.794000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
