{"id": "1193621600776499263", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "386730481502257153", "author_name": "yulina_aa", "author_bot": false, "content": "前三關每關鎖兩隻後三關每關鎖三隻感覺比較好？  這樣既可以靠幾隻高練打到一定的程度也對包包有一定的要求", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:26:06.042000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193621741038215238", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "386730481502257153", "author_name": "yulina_aa", "author_bot": false, "content": "一個界域鎖四隻也組不起來", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:26:39.483000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193621887155191938", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "386730481502257153", "author_name": "yulina_aa", "author_bot": false, "content": "何況24隻就算全都有也只有混沌能跟別人搭  我每個界域都剩下一兩隻到底要怎麼打", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:27:14.320000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193623944197062756", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "會再思考一下。", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T18:35:24.757000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193630683340480633", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 19, "author_id": "170176234070867969", "author_name": "shaynehuang", "author_bot": false, "content": "真的 以目前的數量跟練度真的很難打", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T19:02:11.494000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["386730481502257153"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193621887155191938", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193630683747336274", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181998298282868826", "author_name": "art1_2_3", "author_bot": false, "content": "个人觉得就是现有角色池太浅导致某些角色（比如拉蒙娜）她不同界域的队伍都可能需要，你其它界域也不一定是纯界域阵容所以就算你只是组四个队，像不抽混沌池的玩家真的感觉直接反馈就是一个角色只能用一次肯定不够，再就是24个角色总数量是一个问题，之间的相性也是一个问题，我也赞成不建议第一步就迈这么大，可以队伍数量要求对半砍，或者就是每一期可以选择1~2名角色使用≥2次后再被锁，本来忘却前夜的玩法就比较偏小众，不建议在这方面也采取这种“硬核”的方式，如果制作组的意愿就是想做一个真正意义上不能重复唤醒体和命轮的模式（就是一个性质问题）那我建议减少队伍要求数量，现有阶段角色池太浅这个是硬伤，可以慢慢来，步伐不用一下迈那么大\nPS：其实比较希望是定性在这个“不能重复”上，因为这会非常考验组合搭配", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T19:02:11.591000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193631083623874600", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "170176234070867969", "author_name": "shaynehuang", "author_bot": false, "content": "就算自選足夠好了\n我相信大部分的人應該都還存著至少兩個自選\n畢竟這種東西非常稀有\n以一般人價值觀應該不是會輕易拿去”拓荒”的東西", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T19:03:46.929000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193631191652380702", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 19, "author_id": "456226577798135808", "author_name": "Deleted User", "author_bot": false, "content": "我沒有（悲", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T19:04:12.685000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["170176234070867969"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193631083623874600", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193631390961508422", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "170176234070867969", "author_name": "shaynehuang", "author_bot": false, "content": "現在就出這個限制一個角色使用一次的模式太早了\n才開服一個多月", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T19:05:00.204000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193631904138809354", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "336852868671864832", "author_name": "otonos", "author_bot": false, "content": "半年或一個季度後", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T19:07:02.555000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1193632016898469918", "channel_id": "1193532088788471818", "type": 0, "author_id": "170176234070867969", "author_name": "shaynehuang", "author_bot": false, "content": "我很多界域角色都沒練\n資源投入就沒了也沒有返還機制\n我如果對一個界域不看好我練都不會練他 \n何況我的主力隊伍也還沒練完\n技能 密契要生滿不容易欸", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T19:07:29.439000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-07T19:07:40.682000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193532088788471818", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「無光之境輪轉間隙」的未來改動計劃（第二版）", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
